  <name>Eyedropper</name>
  <summary>A powerful color picker and formatter</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Pick any color from your screen and view it in different formats. Change the picked color or go back to
      a previously picked color from the history list. Generate a list of different shades from the picked color.
    </p>
    <p>Features</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Pick a Color</li>
      <li>Enter a color in Hex-Format</li>
      <li>Parse RGBA/ARGB Hex-Colors</li>
      <li>View colors in Hex, RGB, HSV, HSL, CMYK, XYZ and CIE-Lab format</li>
      <li>Customize which formats appear as well as their order</li>
      <li>Generate a palette of different shades</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
